---
title: Cheese, Chicken Breast and Spinach Penne Bake with Bacon Crumb
description: This Cheese, Chicken Breast and Spinach Penne Bake is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R10_W30_UK_R3416-27_Main_add_low-e6c417b8.jpg
